data.eml:eml: New data on African Cheloninae (Hymenoptera, Braconidae) show a strong biogeographic signal for taxa with spined propodea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Braet, Yves, Rousse, Pascal, Sharkey, Michael (2012): New data on African Cheloninae (Hymenoptera, Braconidae) show a strong biogeographic signal for taxa with spined propodea. Zootaxa 3385: 1-32, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.281743
